title.narrative: Graduation with Resilience to Achieve Sustainable Development (GRAD)

description.narrative: Graduation with Resilience to Achieve Sustainable Development (GRAD) builds on lessons learned from several predecessor USAID projects and activities, including PSNP Plus. An emphasis will be placed on market linkages, access to microfinance, and diversification of household income sources. Additionally, GRAD will also focus on building the resilience of communities through supporting climate change adaptation activities, which will address the high amount of vulnerability in chronically food insecure areas.
